'''拉多斯瓦夫·马耶夫斯基'''（{{lang-pl|'''Radosław Majewski'''}}，{{bd|1986年|12月15日|catIdx=F}}），[[波蘭|波蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場_(足球)|中場]]，效力於[[英冠|英冠]][[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部]]。

==球會生涯==
马耶夫斯基在家鄉球會[[普魯斯科夫火炬足球俱乐部|普魯斯科夫火炬]]展開足球生涯，2007年轉投至[[大波蘭地區格羅濟斯克德斯科博利亞足球俱乐部|格羅濟斯克德斯科博利亞]]。2008年由於球會與[[華沙波蘭人足球俱樂部|華沙波蘭人]]合併，於是他搬到[[華沙|華沙]]踢球，然而由於他的表現平淡及場外生活而飽受批評，會方決定把他外借至英冠球會[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|诺丁汉森林]]。

===诺丁汉森林===
2009年7月23日，马耶夫斯基被外借至诺丁汉森林至球季結束，森林先支付13萬鎊的租借費，另設有約100萬鎊的購買權<ref>{{cite news| title = Polish star joins Forest on loan| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8164390.stm| publisher = BBC| work = BBC Sport| date = 23 July 2009| accessdate = 27 July 2009}}</ref>。马耶夫斯基在诺丁汉森林的表現不錯，8月25日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]賽事中打進在球隊首顆進球，使球隊在加時比賽中勝出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/8203626.stm|title=Nottm Forest 2–1 Middlesbrough|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport|date=25 August 2009|accessdate=26 August 2009|archive-date=2013-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601144721/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_cup/8203626.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月29日對[[德比郡足球俱乐部|德比郡]]賽事中，比賽首分鐘便以30碼遠射取得進球，最終以3-2獲勝<ref>{{cite news|title=Passions boil over as Nottingham Forest take local bragging rights|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/aug/29/championship-nottingham-forest-derby-county|work=The Observer|publisher=Guardian Media Group|date=29 August 2009|accessdate=18 October 2013|first=Jeremy|last=Alexander|archive-date=2009-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090901140020/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/aug/29/championship-nottingham-forest-derby-county|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年1月8日，他打進在球會的第四顆進球，作客以3-1擊敗[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布罗姆维奇]]，使球隊在聯賽積分榜攀至第二名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8439955.stm|title=West Brom 1–3 Nottm Forest|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport|date=8 January 2010 |accessdate=9 January 2010}}</ref>。

2010年5月5日，马耶夫斯基正式轉會至诺丁汉森林<ref>{{cite web| title = Forest wrap up deal for Majewski| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/low/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8661900.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 5 May 2010| accessdate = 7 May 2010| archive-date = 2010-05-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100510044949/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/low/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8661900.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。由於隊友[[刘易斯·麦克古根|刘易斯·麦克古根]]狀態良好，限制了马耶夫斯基的上場時間，使他在新球季只上場了28次<ref name=sb1011>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=49177&season_id=140 |title=Games played by Radoslaw Majewski in 2010/2011 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=11 February 2014 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130202112/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=49177&season_id=140 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該球季只打進兩球，分別是在聯賽對[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|斯旺西城]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Nott'm Forest 3–1 Swansea|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/9021311.stm|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport|date=25 September 2010|accessdate=26 October 2011}}</ref>和[[考文垂足球俱乐部|考文垂]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Nott'm Forest 2–1 Coventry|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/9156245.stm|publisher=BBC|work=BBC Sport|date=9 November 2010|accessdate=26 October 2011}}</ref>。2011/12球季，马耶夫斯基在聯賽共打進六球，首顆進球是作客以3-2擊敗[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普顿]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Rickie Lambert's hat-trick helps Southampton beat Nottingham Forest|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2011/sep/10/southampton-nottingham-forest-championship|publisher=The Guardian|work=guardian.co.uk|location=London|first=Barney|last=Ronay|date=10 September 2011|accessdate=26 October 2011}}</ref>，接著是對[[黑池足球會|黑池]]的半窩利致勝球<ref>{{cite news|title=Blackpool 1 Nottingham Forest 2: Majewski grabs win for Cotterill to shatter Tangerine dreams|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2052159/Blackpool-1-Nottingham-Forest-2-Majewski-bags-win-Cotterill-shatter-Tangerine-dreams.html|publisher=Daily Mail|date=22 October 2011|accessdate=26 October 2011|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820055713/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2052159/Blackpool-1-Nottingham-Forest-2-Majewski-bags-win-Cotterill-shatter-Tangerine-dreams.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使他與隊友[[韋斯·摩根|韋斯·摩根]]一起入選天空體育英冠每週最佳陣容<ref>{{cite news|title=FL Team of the Week|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/12040/7265231/FL-Team-of-the-Week|publisher=British Sky Broadcasting|work=Sky Sports|date=25 October 2011|accessdate=26 October 2011|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803121928/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/12040/7265231/FL-Team-of-the-Week|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年3月31日對[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宫]]比賽中個人大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Crystal Palace 0 Nottingham Forest 3: Hat-trick hero Majewski boosts survival chances|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2123148/Crystal-Palace-0-Nottingham-Forest-3-Hat-trick-hero-Majewski-boosts-survival-chances.html|date=31 March 2012|accessdate=31 March 2012|publisher=Daily Mail|archive-date=2017-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308225022/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2123148/Crystal-Palace-0-Nottingham-Forest-3-Hat-trick-hero-Majewski-boosts-survival-chances.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Crystal Palace vs Nottm Forest: Magic Majewski fires Forest|url=http://www.thisiscroydontoday.co.uk/Crystal-Palace-vs-Nottm-Forest-Magic-Majewski/story-15678761-detail/story.html|publisher=Northcliffe Media|work=thisiscroydontoday.co.uk|date=31 March 2012|accessdate=31 March 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120418124909/http://www.thisiscroydontoday.co.uk/Crystal-Palace-vs-Nottm-Forest-Magic-Majewski/story-15678761-detail/story.html|archivedate=2012年4月18日}}</ref>，再次入選天空體育英冠每週最佳陣容<ref>{{cite news|title=FL Team of the Week|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11689/7648250/FL-Team-of-the-Week|first=James|last=Pearson|publisher=Sky Sports|date=3 April 2012|accessdate=4 April 2012|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803124338/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11689/7648250/FL-Team-of-the-Week|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最後是對[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|赫尔城]]取得進球<ref>{{cite news|title=Hull City 2 Nottingham Forest 1: Tigers sign off at KC with third straight home win|url=http://www.thisishullandeastriding.co.uk/Hull-City-2-Nottingham-Forest-1-Tigers-sign-KC/story-15875099-detail/story.html|publisher=Hull Daily Mail|date=21 April 2012|accessdate=21 April 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120423071116/http://www.thisishullandeastriding.co.uk/Hull-City-2-Nottingham-Forest-1-Tigers-sign-KC/story-15875099-detail/story.html|archivedate=2012年4月23日}}</ref>。

马耶夫斯基在2012/13球季共打進了五球，在2013年2月20日對[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲尔德]]賽事中不但打進他在該賽季的第一球，還戴了帽，使球隊主場以6-1大勝。緊接下來對[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查尔顿竞技]]和[[谢周三足球俱乐部|谢周三]]的比賽中他都取得進球。

